---
title: Garlic Aioli Steak Burgers with Beetroot Relish
description: These steak burgers are easy for little hands to handle, but are paired with a delightful homemade beetroot relish that adults will love, too. The key to this easy supper is slicing the steak as thin as possible to make for easy eating.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5b6b81e2ae08b52d7804fb74-2f03f6ac.jpg
